
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
<font color="#C0C0C0"><em>I say farewell, the final call<br />
I turn and walk away, I leave it all<br />
I find that life regains its glow<br />
But the journey&#8217;s long, the going&#8217;s slow</em></font></p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>A million miles later<br />
I crave a love that&#8217;s greater<br />
Take me home again, ah&#8230;</em></font></p>
<p>Bring me God<br />
Bring me the nostalgia that you took from me<br />
When you sent me away, ah&#8230;</p>
<p>Bring me God<br />
Only the tears can break the rock<br />
That I left behind</p>
<p>Please bring me God<br />
Bring me the tears that you took from me<br />
When you sent me away</p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>Ah&#8230;<br />
Ah&#8230;</em></font></p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>Hear my plea<br />
Take the longing of my heartbeat<br />
Make the melody</em></font></p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>Hear my plea<br />
As it quivers in the tear drops<br />
That you shed for me</em></font></p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>I beg you, hear my plea<br />
Take the longing of my heartbeat<br />
For eternity</em></font></p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>I beg you, hear my plea<br />
The pain, the suffering of today<br />
Tomorrow&#8217;s memory<br />
